00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:22.680
and Hua Xiaohua.

00:04:22.950 --> 00:04:24.240
A member of the Lei Clan.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:25.190
Salutations.

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:28.630
