00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.510
and its strategic location.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:44.950
However, several years ago, Father

00:04:44.950 --> 00:04:46.360
obtained the Skysplitter fragment.

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.270
Many people covet it,

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:49.920
